From: Performance Patch Series
Subject: [PATCH 09/16] 09-batch-information-schema

Batch INFORMATION_SCHEMA queries per dataset to avoid N+1 queries.
BatchFetchColumnsAsync: one query for all columns, grouped by table_name.
BatchFetchConstraintsAsync: one query for all constraints, grouped by table_name.
Pre-fetched rows passed via optional prefetchedRows parameter to
GetColumnSchemaAsync and GetConstraintSchemaAsync (fixes Bug #6).

Co-authored-by: Copilot <223556219+Copilot@users.noreply.github.com>

